{"id":624539841,"lang":"csharp","lang_name":"C#","time":"1 year, 11 months","timestamp":1642756167,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"72 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/624539841/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"39.7 MB","code":"public class Solution {\n    public int RomanToInt(string input) {\n        var dict = new Dictionary<char, int> {\n                { 'I', 1 },\n                { 'V', 5 },\n                { 'X', 10 },\n                { 'L', 50 },\n                { 'C', 100 },\n                { 'D', 500 },\n                { 'M', 1000 },\n            };\n        \n            var integer = 0;\n            \n            if (input != null)\n            {\n                var length = input.Length;\n                var lastNumber = dict[input[length - 1]];\n                integer = lastNumber;\n\n                for (var i = input.Length - 2; i >= 0; i--)\n                {\n                    var current = dict[input[i]];\n                    if (current < lastNumber)\n                    {\n                        integer -= current;\n                    }\n                    else\n                    {\n                        integer += current;\n                    }\n\n                    lastNumber = current;\n                }\n            }\n        \n        return integer;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
